MOVE IN SPECIAL: HALF OFF FIRST MONTH'S RENT!*

Welcome to your dream home nestled in the heart of scenic Ogden, Utah! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom single-family home is a haven of comfort and style, perfectly combining modern amenities with breathtaking mountain views.

There is a $50 application fee per applicant 18 years of age and older.

All HomeRiver Group residents are enrolled in the Resident Benefits Package (RBP) for $39.95 month which includes a convenient option for renters insurance, HVAC air filter delivery (for applicable properties), credit building to help boost your credit score with timely rent payments, $1M Identity Protection, move-in concierge service making utility connection and home service setup a breeze during your move-in, our best-in-class resident rewards program, and much more! More details will be provided upon application.

A refundable security deposit will be due within 24 hours of approval and is equal to one month's rent. An additional deposit may be required depending on qualifying factors. A one-time non-refundable administrative fee of $150.00.

Please note that, once approved, we require that residents take possession of the property within 14 days. If the property is not yet available for move-in, we require that the move-in date be set to within 14 days of the expected availability date.

Pet Policy: Property only allows for 1 dog. Pets accepted on a case by case basis with approval and payment of applicable fees. $300 non-refundable pet fee per pet, and $25 monthly pet inspection fee. Breed restrictions apply. We do not charge additional deposits or fees for documented service/companion animals.

There is a $280 monthly flat fee for all utilities, internet separate. Tenants responsible for yard care.

All information is deemed reliable but not guaranteed and is subject to change.
